      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VERBOSITY (4) is racing well, the latest placing here in slightly tougher class over the same trip. Meets a few from the same race here and expected to go close. HEBEL (5) was one of those, finishing fourth and about a length behind VERBOSITY. Has speed and will take catching. ENTERPRISE LASSIE (7) has switched yards since finishing second six weeks ago over 1800m at Sunshine Coast. Has good early speed and with the claim and inside draw can hit the ground running in the NT. THE GIRL'S BOY (2) missed the placings when resuming two runs back then didn't do any better last start when 10 lengths away in sixth over 1400m at this track. Well placed and can figure in the finish this time. LA VESUVIUS (3) has a good fresh record and expected to run well.",
